Set the difficulty to easy on the options menu.
Time starts when clicking "1P game".
Time ends when the score screen for stage 3 appears.

Controls
Start........... Pause
Left............ Move, jump, or swing left
Right........... Move, jump, or swing right
Down............ Climb down rope, duck
Up.............. Climb up rope
Y button........ Hold items and enemies, use outfit
B button........ Jump, swim
A button........ Change outfit
L or R button... Select outfit

A game over make you restart the stage.